BET’s sinful drama series, Isono, will now air on e.tv giving viewers without Dstv the opportunity to enjoy the show. The drama series, produced by Clive Morris Productions, is set to premiere on the 11th of April, at 8.30pm on weekdays. Isono stars the award-winning and talented actress Nthati Moshesh. She stars alongside the likes of Rami Chuene as Jumima, and Bohang Moeko as Gabriel, who drives the drama. For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.